snippet.title: Commodore C64 - ADIDAS Championship Football © 1990 Smart Egg Software - Gameplay

DESCRIPTION
ADIDAS Championship Football is a Sports game, developed by Smart Egg Software and published by Ocean, which was released in Europe in 1990.
